# Secrets / local env
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Runtime state that should never be published
generated/**/workspace/
generated/**/cache/
generated/**/state/
generated/**/backups/
generated/**/releases/

# Sensitive generated/auth files
generated/**/config/ssh/authorized_keys
generated/**/config/opencode/antigravity-accounts.json
generated/**/config/opencode/auth.json

# Local editor / dependency output
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.DS_Store
**/coverage/
**/*.log
opencode-admin/updater-data/

# Server-side snapshots / helper copies
**/README.github.md
